This is Xanguli - Xanguli Ain't No GUi LIbrary. 
The xanguli project is hosted on http://xanguli.googlecode.com. 
The sourcecode is hosted on github. To get the latest of xanguli do:

git clone git://github.com/surlykke/xanguli.git

To build xanguli, go to the root of the checked-out source and do:

    cmake CMakeList.txt
    make

You'll need to have cmake, make and gcc installed (at least, and probably some other build tools...)


There's no install yet...